						<ol class="space-y-4 text-darkgray">
							<li class="flex">
								<span
									class="bg-secondary text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4 flex-shrink-0">1</span>
								<p><strong>Thermostat Signal:</strong> When your home's temperature drops below the thermostat setting,
									it sends a signal to the furnace to start the heating cycle.</p>
							</li>
							<li class="flex">
								<span
									class="bg-secondary text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4 flex-shrink-0">2</span>
								<p><strong>Heating Elements Activate:</strong> Electricity flows through the heating elements, causing
									them to heat up, similar to how a toaster works.</p>
							</li>
							<li class="flex">
								<span
									class="bg-secondary text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold mr-4 flex-shrink-0">3</span>
